==Description==
The '''Max Revive''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Max Revive has a value of 4 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals. 

==Mine Layout==
The Max Revive appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:MaxReviveMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Max Revives can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Linoone.png|30px]] Linoone, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

